entries.femaleVariant: Oh my God I got the BEST idea! We'll give her a present when we go to their show!
They wrote on their site that they're lovers of expensive tea...
Duuuude, yes! She'll totally remember us after! How nova'd that be?
Just imagine. Few years go by and suddenly oops! We bump into each other on the street...
And she'll be like, "Hey, you're those Night City girls! You made me that AMAZING tea cup!
Hm, idea's solid, 'cept how're we gonna get backstage?
Maybe we could make her a cup? Y'know, like the kind you drink matcha with?
